    <abstract>
      <t>
        The Network File System v4 (NFSv4) allows a client
        to both open a file and be granted a delegation of
        that file.  This grants the client
        the right to cache metadata on the file locally.
        This document presents serveral refinements to
        both the opeing and delegating of the file to the
        client.
      </t>
    </abstract>
